        "action": "Increase lifetime ISA House Price Cap in line with inflation",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The government have spoken about lifetime ISA reforms but have taken no action with regards to this matter. Increase the lifetime ISA house price cap immediately to reflect inflation since it was fixed and annually from now on..",
